name: eu-regionalpolicy-developmentprogrammes
notes:
### About

Overview:

> This section includes summaries of the operational programmes officially adopted by the European Commission at the beginning of a programming period. These documents are available in English, French, German, and in the languages of the country (ies) in question.

### Downloading

Material can be accessed via a series of drop down menus at:

 * <http://ec.europa.eu/regional_policy/country/prordn/index_en.cfm>

### Data

Fields include:

  * Action Priorities
  * Description of the eligible areas 
  * Management and contact details 
  * Financial and Technical information
  * Breakdown of Finances by priority area
    * Priority Area
    * Total Cost
    * EU Contribution
    * Public aid (EC + others)
  * Financial Breakdown by Funds
    * EU Contribution
    * ERDF
    * ESF
    * EAGGF
    * FIFG

### Openness

Free to be re-used as long as attribution is given. The [Copyright notice](http://ec.europa.eu/geninfo/legal_notices_en.htm#copyright) on the European Commission website states:

> Reproduction is authorised, provided the source is acknowledged, save where otherwise stated.

> Where prior permission must be obtained for the reproduction or use of textual and multimedia information (sound, images, software, etc.), such permission shall cancel the above-mentioned general permission and shall clearly indicate any restrictions on use.
